name: PoorPleb
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
PoorPleb ($PP) is a zero utility memecoin on the Ethereum network. PoorPlebs will be able to claim a free airdrop, whales will get NOTHING.

PoorPleb ($PP) is an experiment designed to enrich the many and exclude the few. If you are a small player in some of the most popular memecoins out there you may be eligible to free claim.
